  <trk>
    <name>VIE-L1 — Grossglockner Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from VIE and ride into the Grossglockner. Hit Grossglockner High Alpine Road — 2504m and Salzburg. Loop back to VIE over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
